Error: Missing required argument: target_poi

Usage:
  spacemolt travel <poi_id_or_cached_name>  (use get_system to cache POIs)

Accepted forms:
  spacemolt travel <poi_id_or_cached_name>  (use get_system to cache POIs)
  spacemolt travel target_poi=...
  spacemolt travel --target-poi ...

Example:
  spacemolt travel earth

Next: run "spacemolt get_system" or "spacemolt get_status" or "spacemolt get_commands" to find a valid target_poi.
